    • Method Detail

      • fromCallable

        public static <T> Supplier<T> fromCallable(Callable<? extends T> callable)
        Converts a Callable into a supplier. If the Callable throws a checked exception then that exception will be wrapped in a RuntimeException and propagated.
        Parameters:
        callable - a callable
        Returns:
        a supplier that invokes the specified callable

      • memoize

        public static <T> Supplier<T> memoize(Supplier<T> supplier)
        Returns a supplier that will never invoke the underlying supplier more than once. The result is "memo-ized". All subsequent attempts to get a value from the returned supplier will just get the same memo-ized result of that first invocation.
        Parameters:
        supplier - a supplier
        Returns:
        a supplier that will invoke the specified supplier no more than one time and then memo-ize the result
